            <div class="jumbotron" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                <h1 class="display-4">AIFEX </h1>
                <p class="lead">Improve the quality, efficiency and diversity of your exploratory test sessions</p>
                <hr class="my-4"></hr>
                <p class="main-text text-center">AIFEX - the platform for Exploratory Testing</p>

                <blockquote class="blockquote text-center">
                    <p class="mb-0"><em>``So it is with exploratory testing (ET): simultaneous learning, test design and test execution.''</em></p>
                    <footer class="blockquote-footer">J. Bach</footer>
                </blockquote>
                <div class="text-center">
                <a role="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/account/signin">Try for free</a>
