                        <h3>1</h3>
                        <p><strong>Design</strong> your session by defining its scope and purpose. Give it a name, set the URL of your web application, choose one of our record configuration and give a short description. In less than 2 minutes your new session will be ready to run. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
